data.description: Beautiful home with very large rooms. 5 bed 2 bath 2 living and a study.  Beautiful kitchen with lots of cabinet and counter space.  Large study with doors nestled back away from the bedrooms.  Four bedrooms downstairs including primary bedroom with huge private bath.  The bath has seperate shower and tub.  Very large vanity and double sinks in the primary bath too.  The upstairs bedroom has a HUGE closet and another storage attic area.  You will love the three car garage that opens all the way through.  There is also a storm shelter in the garage. Buyer to verify all info including schools. Motivated Seller
